        public static com.ctre.phoenix.motion.BufferedTrajectoryPointStream createTrajectory(double[][] profile,
                                                                                     double positionToTicks,
                                                                                     double velocityToTicks)
        Creates a trajectory from a profile. Does not assume the units of the profile.
        Parameters:
        profile - The profile as generated from Pathweaver.py (double[][] of {position, velocity, acceleration, duration}.
        positionToTicks - The conversion from units to ticks. This may be the ticks per complete rotation or a conversion from distance per rotation to ticks.
        velocityToTicks - The conversion from units to ticks/100ms.
        Returns:
        The motion profile to follow.
